\section*{Software}
% ============================================================================

All processing used open-source tools with explicit version pinning:
FSL~6.0.7, FreeSurfer~8.2.0, NeuroJAX (JAX~+~Equinox), and
Neurodesk containers for reproducibility. R visualisations use
\texttt{RNifti} and \texttt{knitr}. \LaTeX{} compiled with
\texttt{tectonic}~0.15.

